{"id":3849,"date":"2016-02-05T02:15:20","date_gmt":"2016-02-05T02:15:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/?p=3849"},"modified":"2021-03-01T10:23:12","modified_gmt":"2021-03-01T15:23:12","slug":"meditation-room-a-guide-for-beginners","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/meditation-room-a-guide-for-beginners\/","title":{"rendered":"Start A Meditation Room: 5 Simple Steps and Examples for Beginners!"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>As technology continues to intrude more and more into our lives, the need to create space, relax, and &#8220;chill out&#8221; has increased as well. &nbsp;This can&nbsp;be easily solved by starting your very own meditation room!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"480\" height=\"396\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/df414399b34c2356d43c9a9188374f2292ebffa3eb1f2e5122be08aff351d276.jpg\" alt=\"Funny photo about meditation\" class=\"wp-image-4391\" title=\"Funny photo about meditation\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/df414399b34c2356d43c9a9188374f2292ebffa3eb1f2e5122be08aff351d276.jpg 480w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/df414399b34c2356d43c9a9188374f2292ebffa3eb1f2e5122be08aff351d276-300x248.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/df414399b34c2356d43c9a9188374f2292ebffa3eb1f2e5122be08aff351d276-332x274.jpg 332w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 480px) 100vw, 480px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>A meditation room can help relieve stress and provide the health benefits that come along with stress reduction, such as lowered blood pressure and better sleep at night.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can bring you clarity, awareness, and expanded consciousness if you take the time to practice it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can help when you&#8217;re grieving and when you&#8217;re feeling angry or frustrated.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Meditation can be whatever you want it to be.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can be as simple as closing your office door for 5 minutes while you gather your thoughts or taking 5 minutes in the morning when you wake up or 5 minutes in the evening when you go to bed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It can also be as much as a whole separate meditation room in your house that is designed specifically for calming the&nbsp;mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>If you want to achieve the maximum benefits of having a meditation room, you should have some sort of space that is your own.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The space should be quiet and somewhere that you can be undisturbed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You&#8217;ll want to start by finding a room or even a corner of a room that you can turn into your personal meditation (and\/or yoga) space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s important to note that there are no &#8220;essentials&#8221; for this practice. &nbsp;All you really need is your body and mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>That is the true beauty of the practice. &nbsp;But many people do like to have a few common items present during meditation to help them relax or feel at home in their meditation space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Best Meditation Room Design&nbsp;Ideas:<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Clutter-Free and Worry-Free<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/clutter-free-meditation-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"clutter free meditation room design\" class=\"wp-image-5408\" title=\"clutter free meditation room design\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/clutter-free-meditation-room-design.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/clutter-free-meditation-room-design-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/clutter-free-meditation-room-design-365x244.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>When creating&nbsp;a meditation room, be&nbsp;a minimalist.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You don&#8217;t want a cluttered place to be the space where you are trying to clear your mind.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Avoid using the same rooms that you do work in, especially because the papers and computers will only stand to remind you of the things you need to do that day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Try having a few simple items like a pillow, <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/5-best-yoga-mats-beginner-yogis\/\"  rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">yoga mat<\/a><\/span>, and a plant to start. Only use the essentials until other items become necessary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. Bring nature into the room.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"919\" height=\"678\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/meditation-room-design-with-nature.jpg\" alt=\"meditation room design with nature\" class=\"wp-image-5412\" title=\"meditation room design with nature\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/meditation-room-design-with-nature.jpg 919w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/meditation-room-design-with-nature-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/meditation-room-design-with-nature-768x567.jpg 768w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/meditation-room-design-with-nature-365x269.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 919px) 100vw, 919px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>There&#8217;s something incredibly relaxing about having a life-giving plant in the room with you. It will bring a sense of calm into the room and fresh air as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A peace&nbsp;lily or a Boston fern are great meditation room plants.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Plus, these plants are virtually impossible to kill, so you don&#8217;t have to worry about any dead plants in the room. \ud83d\ude42<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Choose good lighting.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"336\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/bright-and-well-lit-meditation-room-design.jpg\" alt=\"bright and well lit meditation room design\" class=\"wp-image-5410\" title=\"bright and well lit meditation room design\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/bright-and-well-lit-meditation-room-design.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/bright-and-well-lit-meditation-room-design-300x202.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/bright-and-well-lit-meditation-room-design-365x245.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>There is a difference between a stuffy, windowless room and a room full of windows that brings in lots of natural light.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>A big difference.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Natural light brings with it a very calming effect on the body. If at all possible, choose a room that has lots of windows, and you can even open the during your meditation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Keep technology out of the room.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/no-rechnology-in-meditation-room-.jpg\" alt=\"Technology free meditation room\" class=\"wp-image-5413\" title=\"Technology free meditation room\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/no-rechnology-in-meditation-room-.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/no-rechnology-in-meditation-room--300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/no-rechnology-in-meditation-room--365x243.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s been proven that just talking on cell phones raises the natural cortisol levels in the body. A meditation room is about separating from the external noise that surrounds us and pointing our thoughts and feelings internally.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You don&#8217;t want to be pestered. &nbsp;You&#8217;re trying to find peace.&nbsp;Free yourself of using any technology, and leave all &#8220;devices&#8221; at the door!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. The more open, the better.<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" src=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/shutterstock_202373446.jpg\" alt=\"Meditation room design in nature\" class=\"wp-image-5406\" title=\"Meditation room design in nature\" srcset=\"https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/shutterstock_202373446.jpg 500w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/shutterstock_202373446-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/avocadu.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2016\/02\/shutterstock_202373446-365x243.jpg 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Listen, we totally understand where you are coming from. We don&#8217;t assume you can afford some mansion with a Japanese gazebo right outside.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All you should focus on is that the room has plenty of&nbsp;space. The more &#8220;open&#8221; the room, the better you will feel. \ud83d\ude42 Meditation is not only about the room but also the awareness of your mind, body, and senses.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#8217;s believed that optimal meditation is achieved when all of your senses are in harmony with one another.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Add These Meditation Room Supplies for Your 5&nbsp;Senses:<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Smell<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B0080KKAB6\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B0080KKAB6&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=VDUZ4VXEYMAELVFP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B0080KKAB6&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20\" alt=\"Meditation room flower for senses\" title=\"Meditation room flower for senses\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Smells can be very powerful on the mind and body. This <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B0080KKAB6\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B0080KKAB6&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=HLSKWUXDMECLZIIA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">incense burner<\/a><\/span> is great because it doubles as a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B00DUF1ANI\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00DUF1ANI&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=FX537H4VGM6JHAVN\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">tealight<\/a><\/span> holder as well.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many people also opt for <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B004FP9P0M\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B004FP9P0M&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=EX2N2MFBOBBVXPKD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">incense<\/a><\/span>, but a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B000YBFJQU\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B000YBFJQU&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=L7RNEB5JJR5F77IR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">candle<\/a><\/span> can do the job just the same if you find it easier to use.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Sound<\/span><\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B003JMQ640\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003JMQ640&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=4ZIZHAB2BZEBIDA6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B003JMQ640&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20\" alt=\"Meditation room bell for calming sounds\" title=\"Meditation room bell for calming sounds\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">.<\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Many people use a meditation bell or some type of music to signify the beginning and end of their meditation period.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A very common tool for this purpose is a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B003JMQ640\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003JMQ640&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=YJX475THG5DLHVSA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">Tibetan Meditation Singing Bowl<\/a><\/span>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is inscribed with a hand-etched Buddhist prayer or peace.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Sight<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B003TYEYK6\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003TYEYK6&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=LCWZM2BLJTQ44OWW\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B003TYEYK6&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20\" alt=\"Statue of Buddha for you meditation room. \" title=\"Statue of Buddha for you meditation room. \"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>A prayer or <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B003TYEYK6\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B003TYEYK6&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=FXIYQAUV6ZJIG3NV\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">meditation statue<\/a><\/span> is a symbol and reminder&nbsp;of your affirmations and what you are there for.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Buddhas and peace and harmony statues are popular but don&#8217;t forget that this is about you and what you want to make it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want a <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B00K4UD350\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00K4UD350&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=4K544WP2JJKZYW7Y\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">meditating frog statue<\/a><\/span> in your meditation space, then go for it!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Touch<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B00UWAPVCA\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00UWAPVCA&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=BN4VBS5Y26CFGTF7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/ws-na.amazon-adsystem.com\/widgets\/q?_encoding=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B00UWAPVCA&amp;Format=_SL250_&amp;ID=AsinImage&amp;MarketPlace=US&amp;ServiceVersion=20070822&amp;WS=1&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20\" alt=\"Mala beads for a meditation room\" title=\"Mala beads for a meditation room\"\/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Traditional <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B00UWAPVCA\/ref=as_li_qf_sp_asin_il_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00UWAPVCA&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=GB32DKM4YMOAG2EP\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noreferrer noopener\">mala meditation beads<\/a><\/span>, also known as Buddhist prayer beads,&nbsp; have 108 beads used for keeping count of mantra meditations.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>A &#8220;mantra&#8221; is simply your own personal affirmation or commitment to yourself. They are also called Buddhist prayer beads and are a great addition to any meditation room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Taste<\/strong><\/span><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"http:\/\/www.amazon.com\/gp\/product\/B00404XCLQ\/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=9325&amp;creativeASIN=B00404XCLQ&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=avo-meditationroom-20&amp;linkId=ZJYBGWXSXOUY7OW3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow sponsored noopener noreferrer\"><img decod